{"id":150601,"type":1,"name":"Behind master","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/f0/75/150601_3LxM5.jpg","summary":"清海在树林里迷了路，失足掉下山崖，当他在昏迷状态是，看见一个“少年”向他走来。“你到天狗的住处有什么事吗？”“少年”问道。当他再醒来时发现，“少年”变成了“少女”，在他迷惑时，知道了“少年”叫佐助，是一名忍者。然后和我们的主角佐助开始了对一踪离奇的少女失踪案展开了调查从而展开了如影随形这个正宗战国传奇的篇章.先申明，此佐助非彼佐助（火影忍者）也，虽然也是忍者，但是故事完全不同哦。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>如影随形</li><li><span>册数: </span>6</li><li><span>作者: </span><a href=\"/person/19949\">坂本あきら</a></li><li><span>出版社: </span><a href=\"/person/497\">スクウェア・エニックス</a></li><li><span>连载杂志: </span><a href=\"/person/8240\">月刊ガンガンWING</a></li><li><span>发售日: </span>2003-05</li>","collection":{"wish":2,"collect":1,"doing":1,"dropped":1},"tags":[{"name":"CC","count":1},{"name":"坂本あきら","count":1},{"name":"2003","count":1},{"name":"已完结","count":1},{"name":"漫画系列","count":1},{"name":"漫画","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":19949,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/b6/cc/19949_prsn_9Qk3s.jpg","name":"坂本あきら","desc":"作者"},{"id":497,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/e6/d9/497_prsn_z3Upo.jpg","name":"史克威尔·艾尼克斯","desc":"出版社"},{"id":8240,"image":"","name":"月刊GANGAN WING","desc":"连载杂志"}],"comic":[{"id":150595,"name":"Behind master (1)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/1a/4c/150595_i7E9Q.jpg"},{"id":150596,"name":"Behind master (2)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/93/02/150596_3nMkH.jpg"},{"id":150597,"name":"Behind master (3)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/dd/f3/150597_KQRV4.jpg"},{"id":150598,"name":"Behind master (4)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/40/5b/150598_tJcO0.jpg"},{"id":150599,"name":"Behind master (5)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/75/47/150599_jp.jpg"},{"id":150600,"name":"Behind master (6)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/9f/37/150600_2CDy2.jpg"}]}